{"tid":1487313,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"潛水rescue diver有冇用？","createTime":"2019-08-19T08:16:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T12:18:32.000Z","uid":76413,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"8de4742f277f2fe88e65ea827ece8b1640a1b997","tid":1487313,"uid":76413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T08:16:15.000Z","msg":"話說想9月尾到去龜島考ow同aow。<br />\n咁我見到佢有個package 係ow+aow+rescue diver，<br />\n而感覺rescue diver好似又真係幾有用，必要時可能救到自己同其他人條命仔咁上下。<br />\n不過因為佢又貴多幾千，<br />\n所以想問下rescue diver呢個course 你覺得幾有用？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n順便想問下9月尾10月有冇人想一齊去學潛水，毒撚未試過單丁出國有少少淆底<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69618349df67335ecc316284287e62ee1bc83b99","tid":1487313,"uid":187510,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T08:18:09.000Z","msg":"一次過考到Rescue 係可以 但你根本無經驗 而且RESCUE唔易考<br />\n我唔知佢咩準則 但一次過考晒就似係垃圾教練亂發牌"},{"pid":"e017b319e57e546140d1cec9238e77d709383448","tid":1487313,"uid":306434,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T08:20:54.000Z","msg":"不建議咁快學rescue diver<br />\n<br />\n學完OW同AOW之後需要累積一定經驗你先叫有一定技術照顧自己，rescue diver係照顧別人既技術，建議玩番起碼40個DIVE，搞掂自己先諗照顧其他DIVER吧"},{"pid":"2fe29a2355c0c8a50b175c098e3360acc4f7f74d","tid":1487313,"uid":306434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e017b319e57e546140d1cec9238e77d709383448","tid":1487313,"uid":306434,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T08:20:54.000Z","msg":"不建議咁快學rescue diver<br />\n<br />\n學完OW同AOW之後需要累積一定經驗你先叫有一定技術照顧自己，rescue diver係照顧別人既技術，建議玩番起碼40個DIVE，搞掂自己先諗照顧其他DIVER吧"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T08:22:59.000Z","msg":"道理如同準備學游水既人唔會一唔一次過學埋拯溺"},{"pid":"94a488371eb47c76abb902530b3d931d3a432868","tid":1487313,"uid":76413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e017b319e57e546140d1cec9238e77d709383448","tid":1487313,"uid":306434,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T08:20:54.000Z",